{"title":"PNW Components LTD Silver Dropper Posts Are On the Way","link":"https://theradavist.com/pnw-components-ltd-silver-dropper-posts-are-on-the-way/","date":1727101351000,"content":"<p><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2000\" height=\"1334\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/09/PNW-Components-LTD-Silver-Dropper-Posts-1.jpg?fit=1200,1334&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/09/PNW-Components-LTD-Silver-Dropper-Posts-1.jpg?w=2000&amp;quality=75 2000w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/09/PNW-Components-LTD-Silver-Dropper-Posts-1.jpg?resize=1200,800&amp;quality=75 1200w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/09/PNW-Components-LTD-Silver-Dropper-Posts-1.jpg?resize=768,512&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/09/PNW-Components-LTD-Silver-Dropper-Posts-1.jpg?resize=1536,1025&amp;quality=75 1536w\" /></p>\n<p><em>John got his <a href=\"https://theradavist.com/how-to-silver-dropper-post/\" target=\"_blank\">anodizing-stripping hands</a> on one of the new <a href=\"https://theradavist.com/pnw-components-silver-stanchion-dropper/\" target=\"_blank\">PNW Components LTD Silver Dropper Posts</a> ahead of their launch. Read on below for all the details on how you can snatch one too!</em><span></span></p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2000\" height=\"1334\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/09/PNW-Components-LTD-Silver-Dropper-Posts-2.jpg?fit=1200,1334&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/09/PNW-Components-LTD-Silver-Dropper-Posts-2.jpg?w=2000&amp;quality=75 2000w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/09/PNW-Components-LTD-Silver-Dropper-Posts-2.jpg?resize=1200,800&amp;quality=75 1200w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/09/PNW-Components-LTD-Silver-Dropper-Posts-2.jpg?resize=768,512&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/09/PNW-Components-LTD-Silver-Dropper-Posts-2.jpg?resize=1536,1025&amp;quality=75 1536w\" /></p>\n<p>When John posted that <a href=\"https://theradavist.com/how-to-silver-dropper-post/\" target=\"_blank\">he stripped his Wolf Tooth dropper’s stanchion</a> and later <a href=\"https://theradavist.com/bike-hack-strip-entire-dropper-post/\" target=\"_blank\">the whole dropper post</a> on <a href=\"https://theradavist.com/mone-bikes-sb2-review/\" target=\"_blank\">his Moné SB2</a>, we didn’t think anyone thought companies would hear the horn of Gondor for more silver droppers. Well, PNW Components heard the call and, at <a href=\"https://theradavist.com/pnw-components-silver-stanchion-dropper/\" target=\"_blank\">Sea Otter this year</a>, previewed their new LTD Silver Loam dropper posts. Now, five months later, we have some news on this front.</p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2000\" height=\"1334\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/09/2024-MADE-BIke-Show-Pine-Rigid-29er-14.jpg?fit=1200,1334&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/09/2024-MADE-BIke-Show-Pine-Rigid-29er-14.jpg?w=2000&amp;quality=75 2000w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/09/2024-MADE-BIke-Show-Pine-Rigid-29er-14.jpg?resize=1200,800&amp;quality=75 1200w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/09/2024-MADE-BIke-Show-Pine-Rigid-29er-14.jpg?resize=768,512&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/09/2024-MADE-BIke-Show-Pine-Rigid-29er-14.jpg?resize=1536,1025&amp;quality=75 1536w\" /><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2000\" height=\"1334\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/09/2024-MADE-BIke-Show-Pine-Rigid-29er-3.jpg?fit=1200,1334&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/09/2024-MADE-BIke-Show-Pine-Rigid-29er-3.jpg?w=2000&amp;quality=75 2000w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/09/2024-MADE-BIke-Show-Pine-Rigid-29er-3.jpg?resize=1200,800&amp;quality=75 1200w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/09/2024-MADE-BIke-Show-Pine-Rigid-29er-3.jpg?resize=768,512&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/09/2024-MADE-BIke-Show-Pine-Rigid-29er-3.jpg?resize=1536,1025&amp;quality=75 1536w\" /></p>\n<p>The good news is that the LTD Silver Loam Dropper Posts are finally arriving on September 26th. PNW Components will have both the Loam Droppers (MTB) and the Rainier 27.2 x 125 mm (gravel/touring/road) – which we teased in our <a href=\"https://theradavist.com/2024-made-bike-show-we-are-one-bikepacking-wheels/\" target=\"_blank\">MADE coverage on the Pine rigid 29er</a> – available in limited quantities.</p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2000\" height=\"1334\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/09/PNW-Components-LTD-Silver-Dropper-Posts-5.jpg?fit=1200,1334&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/09/PNW-Components-LTD-Silver-Dropper-Posts-5.jpg?w=2000&amp;quality=75 2000w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/09/PNW-Components-LTD-Silver-Dropper-Posts-5.jpg?resize=1200,800&amp;quality=75 1200w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/09/PNW-Components-LTD-Silver-Dropper-Posts-5.jpg?resize=768,512&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/09/PNW-Components-LTD-Silver-Dropper-Posts-5.jpg?resize=1536,1025&amp;quality=75 1536w\" /><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2000\" height=\"1334\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/09/PNW-Components-LTD-Silver-Dropper-Posts-3.jpg?fit=1200,1334&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/09/PNW-Components-LTD-Silver-Dropper-Posts-3.jpg?w=2000&amp;quality=75 2000w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/09/PNW-Components-LTD-Silver-Dropper-Posts-3.jpg?resize=1200,800&amp;quality=75 1200w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/09/PNW-Components-LTD-Silver-Dropper-Posts-3.jpg?resize=768,512&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/09/PNW-Components-LTD-Silver-Dropper-Posts-3.jpg?resize=1536,1025&amp;quality=75 1536w\" /></p>\n<p>Here’s the bad news: There are more people on the waitlist than droppers coming in. This doesn’t mean they will sell out, but they might. Keep in mind that PNW Components does have preorders with dealers as well.</p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2000\" height=\"1334\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/09/PNW-Components-LTD-Silver-Dropper-Posts-4.jpg?fit=1200,1334&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/09/PNW-Components-LTD-Silver-Dropper-Posts-4.jpg?w=2000&amp;quality=75 2000w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/09/PNW-Components-LTD-Silver-Dropper-Posts-4.jpg?resize=1200,800&amp;quality=75 1200w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/09/PNW-Components-LTD-Silver-Dropper-Posts-4.jpg?resize=768,512&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/09/PNW-Components-LTD-Silver-Dropper-Posts-4.jpg?resize=1536,1025&amp;quality=75 1536w\" /></p>\n<p>Anyone who has joined the LTD Silver Dropper waitlist will be eligible for preorder on September 26th, PNW will launch the posts to the public on the following Monday, September 30th.</p>\n<p>We might be giving away one of these as well!</p>\n<p>Keep your eyes peeled on <a href=\"https://www.pnwcomponents.com/\" target=\"_blank\">PNW Components</a>!</p>\n<p>The post <a href=\"https://theradavist.com/pnw-components-ltd-silver-dropper-posts-are-on-the-way/\">PNW Components LTD Silver Dropper Posts Are On the Way</a> appeared first on <a href=\"https://theradavist.com\">The Radavist</a>.</p>","author":"John Watson","siteTitle":"The Radavist","siteHash":"96eb481d8084f04a4602bac57874ba717baf56b758f45547b5caf2312da766ef","entryHash":"47fdc31576d9494ac24401d375aa32ea0d7a91b122576d0350241ab49dd132de","category":"Cycling"}